04)------SubqueryAlias: t
05)--------Projection:
06)----------Filter: substr(CAST(md5(CAST(generate_series().value AS Utf8View)) AS Utf8View), Int64(1), Int64(32)) IS NOT NULL OR Boolean(NULL)
07)------------TableScan: generate_series() projection=[value]
